name: Room near MBTA Forest Hills w/ private living room
neighborhood_overview: Arnold Arboretum is only a few minute walk, pizza store like Domino's is nearby. Target and supermarkets are less than 1 mile away.
description:
Great location, conveniently located just steps away from 8 bus routes, near Forest Hills T Station. Walk to Arnold Arboretum.
Newly renovated kitchen, bright and spacious bedroom with private living room in Boston neighborhood of Roslindale. It comes with a queen size bed, hardwood floor, comfortable living room with smart TV and full size convertible sofa bed and fast Gig speed Internet. Personal fridge inside your room and no sharing with others.
Keyless self check-in for your convenience.

The space
This room is on the first floor of a smoke-free/ pet-free two-family house.
Shared kitchen and bathroom, coin-operated laundry in the basement.
The room is fairly large with a private entrance independent of the rest of the apartment.
